  Accept:
  - Thank you so much
  - Thank you for giving me a place to stay
  - Oh really, thank you so much
  QuestionIDPass:
  - I have my ID government issued. Please check again
  - But my ID is government issued. Can you check again please?
  QuestionIDFailed:
  - Oh wait did i not have my ID government issued? My bad
  - I forgot that my ID is not government issued. My bad
  QuestionFakeID:
  - Oh.. You caught my disguise
  - Yikes. You caught my disguise. You got me.
  QuestionLetterPassed:
  - I already have my letter government issued. Please check again.
  - But my letter is government issued. Can you check again please?
  QuestionLetterFailed:
  - Oh.. I think i forgot to make my letter government issued. Sorry about that.
  - Wait.. My Letter Isn't government issued?? My fault
  QuestionApplicationPassed:
  - My Application is Government issued. Please check again
  - But my application is government issued. Kindly check again
  QuestionApplicationFailed:
  - Oh its not government issued? My bad
  - Oh you need to have it government issued as well? oops
  QuestionApplicationIDFailed:
  - Oh right. I didn't read the small text below
  - Oh really?? I thought IDs without government issued is allowed
  QuestionDataPassed:
  - I already registered for the shelter today. Please check again.
  - I think there has been a mistake, because i already registered for the shelter
    today.
  QuestionDataFailed:
  - I did not register because I just got discharged from the hospital, and i need
    a place to stay ASAP.
  - I didn't have time to register because I had to flee a violent situation.
  - I did not register because i've never been homeless before, and i didn't know
    that we need to register in the first place.
  RejectApplicationConfirmed:
  - Thanks for the application. I'll fill it in as soon as possible
  - Thank you for this application. I will return it once i have filled this in.
  RejectApplicationFirstUnwanted:
  - I don't think I need to fill in this application. My letter is already government
    issued.
  - I'm not filling in this form. I already have my letter government issued
  RejectApplicationSecondUnwanted:
  - This is ridiculous. You are trying to push me away
  - Fine. I don't have the energy to argue with you today. I'm leaving
  RejectFirstComplete:
  - But i have everything set. Shouldn't you let me in?
  - I already fullfilled everything. Please let me stay
  RejectSecondComplete:
  - ...Fine, i'll just find another shelter
  - I can't believe i get rejected, after everything I did.
  RejectFirstIncomplete:
  - Even if my data is incomplete, can you at least do something about it?
  - Please help me find any alternatives, i just need a place to stay.
  RejectSecondIncomplete:
  - You're not even trying your best to give people shelter..
  - ...Fine, i'll just find another shelter
  MultipleMistakes:
  - I am not cooperating with you anymore. I'm leaving
  - You really can't do your job properly huh? Fine, i'll just find another shelter.
